OL,6,FMotorists at Gatwick Airport have
OL,7,Fexpressed their frustration with the
OL,8,Fincreased drop-off charge, Good
OL,9,FMorning Britain reports
OL,11,FAs of today, passengers being dropped
OL,12,Foff at Gatwick Airport must now pay
OL,13,F#10, as other UK airports also
OL,14,Fincrease their drop-off fees for the
OL,15,Fnew year.
OL,17,FBritain's second-busiest airport has
OL,18,Fbecome the first in the UK to charge
OL,19,F#10 for passenger drop-offs, a 43%
OL,20,Fincrease on the previous #7 fee.
