OL,6,FGatwick's new charge is now the
OL,7,Fhighest of any UK airport and marks a
OL,8,Fdoubling in price in less than five
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FWhen the fee was introduced in April
OL,12,F2021, it was #5, rising to #6 in
OL,13,FJanuary 2024 and #7 in May 2025.
OL,15,FPassengers can be dropped off without
OL,16,Fcharge in long-stay car parks and
OL,17,Fcatch a free shuttle bus to the
OL,18,Fterminals, a Gatwick spokesperson said.
OL,20,FBlue badge holders will remain exempt
OL,21,Ffrom Gatwick's drop-off fee.
